title: 22 Young Adult Novels of April 2014 by Various Authors
description:
List:

1. Dreams of Gods & Monsters by Laini Taylor
2. Dorothy Must Die by Danielle Paige
3. Illusion by Sherrilyn Kenyon
4. Sea of Shadows by Kelley Armstrong
5. The Forever Song by Julie Kagawa
6. The Taking by Kimberly Derting
7. Toxic Heart by Theo Lawrence
8. Dear Killer by Katherine Ewell
9. Don't Look Back by Jennifer L. Armentrout
10. Far From You by Tess Sharpe
11. Pointe by Brandy Colbert
12. Prisoner of Night and Fog by Anne Blankman
13. Rebel Belle by Rachel Hawkins
14. Salvage by Alexandra Duncan
15. Love Letters to the Dead by Ava Dellaira
16. Plus One by Elizabeth Fama
17. Sweet Reckoning by Wendy Higgins
18. The Geography of You and Me by Jennifer E. Smith
19. The Here and Now by Ann Brashares
20. The Ring and the Crown by Melissa de La Cruz
21. To All the Boys I've Loved Before by Jenny Han
22. What I Thought Was True by Huntley Fitzpatrick
